Package model

Class ShowTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.ShowTime
  • public class ShowTime
extends java.lang.Object
    This Model class contains all information of a showtime - including the name of the cineplex, the cinema ID, the movie name, the date and time, the row number, the column number, and the seating arrangement.
    Version:
    1.0
